content:
Moraaneesho kurishaalum-maathaavin praarththhanayaalum
Kopatthin dandangalle nee-maayichillaathaakkename.
Aadaamyare ettaan sleebaa-kovaniyaakkiyavan dhanyan
Thanmoolam nibi sahadenmaar-shleehanmaarum rakshitharaayu
Sleebaaye! Vaazhuka vaanil sleebaaye! Vaazhuka bhoovil
Sleebaa dayaraa pallllikalle-kottaykkoppam kaakkatte.
Moraaneesho! Nin sleebaa-nyangallkkennum sangketham
Saatthaanilninnum kaatth-sleebaa svargam nalkatte.
